<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Conteúdo Restrito</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
}

body{
height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
background:radial-gradient(circle at top,#1a1a1a,#0d0d0d 60%);
overflow:hidden;
}

.card{
width:92%;
max-width:430px;
background:#181818;
border-radius:28px;
padding:38px;
text-align:center;
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);
box-shadow:0 20px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.55);
animation:card .6s ease;
}

@keyframes card{
from{
opacity:0;
transform:translateY(40px) scale(.95);
}
to{
opacity:1;
transform:translateY(0) scale(1);
}
}

.icon{
width:74px;
height:74px;
margin:auto;
background:#2b2512;
border-radius:20px;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
font-size:38px;
color:#FFD84C;
}

h1{
margin-top:26px;
font-size:36px;
font-weight:700;
color:white;
}

p{
margin-top:18px;
color:#8c8c8c;
line-height:30px;
font-size:18px;
}

.buttons{
margin-top:38px;
display:flex;
gap:16px;
}

button{
height:60px;
border:none;
flex:1;
border-radius:18px;
font-size:18px;
font-weight:700;
cursor:pointer;
transition:.25s;
}

.ok{
background:#20d462;
color:white;
box-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(32,212,98,.55);
animation:glow 2s infinite;
}

@keyframes glow{
0%{
box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(32,212,98,.25);
}
50%{
box-shadow:0 0 35px rgba(32,212,98,.8);
}
100%{
box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(32,212,98,.25);
}
}

.ok:hover{
transform:translateY(-2px);
}

.exit{
background:#2b2b2b;
color:#a0a0a0;
}

.exit:hover{
background:#353535;
}

.footer{
margin-top:28px;
font-size:12px;
letter-spacing:2px;
color:#555;
text-transform:uppercase;
}

@media(max-width:450px){

h1{
font-size:30px;
}

p{
font-size:16px;
line-height:26px;
}

button{
height:56px;
font-size:17px;
}

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

<div class="icon">
⚠️
</div>

<h1>Conteúdo Restrito</h1>

<p>
Este conteúdo é destinado exclusivamente para maiores de 18 anos.
Ao continuar, você confirma possuir idade legal.
</p>

<div class="buttons">

<button class="ok"
onclick="window.location.href='https://telegram.me/+nRllUPqTH49lZDJh'">
Tenho +18
</button>

<button class="exit"
onclick="window.location.href='https://telegram.me/+nRllUPqTH49lZDJh'">
Sair
</button>

</div>

<div class="footer">
VERIFICAÇÃO OBRIGATÓRIA
</div>

</div>

</body>

</html>
